data.meta_description: Name: Tsukishima Kirari Age: 14 Occupation: Idol/Student Description: Kirari is a very gluttonous girl who loves eating. After meeting Seiji-kun of the SHIPS music band, she falls in love with him and is determined to become an idol. She is beautiful, but rather empty-headed.
data.text:
Name: Tsukishima Kirari

Age: 14

Occupation: Idol/Student

Description: Kirari is a very gluttonous girl who loves eating. After meeting Seiji-kun of the SHIPS music band, she falls in love with him and is determined to become an idol. She is beautiful, but rather empty-headed.
